    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e6e8000000000089eb96",
      "text": " [imdkm]、[tofubeats]と共に京都で「セプテンバー九月」というグループを結成して公演を行っていた",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854184,
      "updated": 1777854576
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e7a4000000000089eb9e",
      "text": " [Maltine Records]所属",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854373,
      "updated": 1777854577
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e7a5000000000089eb9f",
      "text": " [DE DE MOUSE]、[梅沢和木]と親交があった",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854373,
      "updated": 1777854789
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e95f000000000089ebab",
      "text": " TankManiaで出会った[さつき が てんこもり]に音楽を教えていた",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854815,
      "updated": 1777854917
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e96f000000000089ebac",
      "text": " \t[http://blog.livedoor.jp/satukinpo/archives/834679.html 連続エネルギー弾＝負けフラグ:imoutoid（ファミコン宇宙人）]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854831,
      "updated": 1777854906
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e871000000000089eba0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854577,
      "updated": 1777854577
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e8b9000000000089eba4",
      "text": "[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854649,
      "updated": 1777854649
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e8ba000000000089eba5",
      "text": " [夭折]と聞いてまず思い浮かぶ人物",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854649,
      "updated": 1777854666
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e8cb000000000089eba7",
      "text": " \t[滝廉太郎]よりも何年も早く亡くなった芸術家なんて彼くらいだろう",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854667,
      "updated": 1777854694
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e8e7000000000089eba8",
      "text": " [上伊那ぼたん、酔へる姿は百合の花]で紹介されている",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854695,
      "updated": 1777854706
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e8f3000000000089eba9",
      "text": " \t[https://posfie.com/@hoagecko/p/GRuXkVQ 「上伊那ぼたん」imoutoidを6巻で言及 - あかね「tofubeats経由で」 - posfie]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854707,
      "updated": 1777854740
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e917000000000089ebaa",
      "text": " \t\t上記の拙まとめを参照のこと",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854743,
      "updated": 1777854999
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e9ee000000000089ebad",
      "text": " [ころんば]に並ぶインターネット散逸音楽だと思う",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854959,
      "updated": 1777855006
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7ea00000000000089ebae",
      "text": " \tまあこちらは遺族の方が公式にアーカイブしているから多少事情は違うが",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854976,
      "updated": 1777854993
    },
    {
      "id": "69f7e8bc000000000089eba6",
      "text": " [kawaii future bass]の始祖",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777854652,
      "updated": 1777855034
    },
